EN: We drove through a rugged mountain road.

ZH: 雨后的山路非常泥泞难行。
EN: The mountain road is very muddy and difficult to pass after the rain.

ZH: 在山路上采风，感受大自然的美好。
EN: Enjoy the beauty of nature on the mountain road.

ZH: 独自走在山路上，享受宁静的时光。
EN: Walking alone on the mountain road, enjoying the peaceful time.

ZH: 夜晚的山路看起来很神秘。
EN: The mountain road looks mysterious at night.

ZH: 山路上有许多神秘的传说。
EN: There are many mysterious legends on the mountain road.

ZH: 在山路上遇到了一只小松鼠。
EN: I met a little squirrel on the mountain road.

ZH: 山路两旁开满了野花。
EN: Wildflowers bloom on both sides of the mountain road.

ZH: 徒步穿越这段山路需要一整天的时间。
EN: It takes a whole day to hike through this mountain road.

